text: Welcome home! This house is totally renovated and is move in ready. The exterior as been painted with all new gutters and duct work. The wood floors have been restored to the original look. New drywall with a new cedar accent wall, false ceiling removed and original ceilings restored. Crawl space insulation replaced as well as all interior. Front door restored and all interior painted. New cabinets and appliances in kitchen. New bathroom fixtures, plumbing, electrical, furnace, hot water heater, and lighting. The sewer line has also been flushed. The unattached garage is great with storing a car and have a small work area on the side. The laundry was an addition and has great big windows and a pantry. Come check it out.

Escape to the serene woods of Point Roberts to this quaint home situated on a private lot, featuring 1 bed and 1 bath. This well-maintained property offers a bright open concept layout with large windows and vaulted ceilings with beautiful wood paneling. Views from every window of beautiful evergreen trees, and a large covered deck that could be enjoyed every season. Don't miss out on this great turn-key property in the heart of Point Roberts. Only 30 minutes from Vancouver, the perfect vacation oasis or all year around home.

Discover Rustic Luxury in this Mountain Retreat! Meticulously maintained 'True Log Homes' log cabin in Glacier's Snowline gated community. Ideal personal getaway and turn-key short term rental investment, fully furnished! Three bed septic w/2 proper bedrooms + sleeping loft + multiple sleeping spaces for guests. Space for 3rd bedroom on main. Recent updates include NEW: flooring throughout, hot tub + gazebo, generator, SS refrigerator & range, couches (two w/ pull-out beds), electric wall space heaters, propane tank & ceiling fans. Complete w/ dry sauna upstairs. Huge deck w/views of Mt. Baker, w/heater is ideal for outdoor entertainment. Snowline amenities: pool, clubhouse, play/sports area, tennis courts, & full time manager/security.

Discover your dream home with this beautifully updated 3 bed/2 bath gem! The spacious primary bedroom boasts a luxurious 4-piece en-suite, perfect for unwinding. The updated kitchen features sleek stainless steel appliances and ample storage, ideal for the home chef. Vaulted ceilings create an airy feel throughout the living areas. Let your imagination run wild w/the large bonus room upstairs! Could be a playroom, TV room, craft space, etc. Step outside to your oasis: a massive deck perfect for entertaining, a relaxing hot tub, and a fully fenced yard with a dedicated dog run & firepit. This home offers comfort and convenience. Dont miss out on this fantastic opportunity in a great location!

Best Price per SQ FT in One of Ferndales Most Desirable Neighborhoods! Stunning Custom Home on a Shy 1/4 Acre Corner Landscaped Lot. This House was Intentionally Situated to Give You Amazing Views of Mt. Baker from Almost Every Room. You'll Love the Spacious Kitchen, Two Decks, and Office on the Main Floor. Upstairs, You have the Owner's Suite with a 5-Piece Bath and a Picture-Perfect View of Mt. Baker, along with Three Other Bedrooms and Full Bath. The Lower Level is 1, 075 SqFt with Brand New Carpets, Zero Stairs, a Full Bathroom and it's Own Private Entrance (Possible MIL). RV/Boat Parking too. Many Upgrades including Landscape Lighting and a Brand New LG Refrigerator and Range with Air Fryer.

This 9.65-acre flat parcel in the PNW is perfect for outdoor enthusiasts. Located across the street from, but not affiliated with, Meadow Mist private airpark. The flat terrain is ideal for building your own custom home, farm, or maybe your very own helicopter pad with hanger and other amenities. Aviation friendly neighborhood. Surrounded by natural beauty & mountain views, this property offers a peaceful retreat while serving as an ideal aviation-friendly base. Breathtaking trails throughout the property give it easy walking access. Great value in the trees on the property, could help offset some costs of making your dream take flight. 15 Minutes to Bellingham, 90 to Vancouver, & 2hrs to Seattle.

Just shy 2 acres, 2 lots, property has been short platted! An opportunity to rehab. existing small home or build 1, potentially, 2 homes. Outside city limits. The expensive, hard work has been done! Wetlands delineation study complete, new 3-bed septic permit on file with the county, the existing 2-bedroom septic in place-installed 2018, new survey is complete, clean air & no asbestos permits/reports issued, demolition permit issued, water district 2 already in use & approved by the county, temp. power pole installed & approved by county, round 1 of building permitting has been done, as well as engineered plans for a 2, 683 sq ft 3 bed, 2 bath w/den & bonus room. Tons of debris has been removed from the property. Use caution when viewing.
nearby_schools: Northwest Educational Service District 189, Bellingham Public Schools

text: Ready for a great property, complete with building plans and a permitted septic design? Check out this beautiful .44 acre property in the Glenhaven Lakes Community! Home plans and structural engineered drawings are for a 2, 501 sq ft 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home with a fully contained in-law suite and an 11' x 21' covered deck area. Located just steps away from the Treasure Island Lake access, enjoy all the amenities that Glenhaven has to offer. There are 2 lakes to enjoy fishing, seasonal pool, clubhouse, kayaking and battery operated boating.

Charming home on a .27-acre, fully-fenced lot with beautiful landscaping. The kitchen boasts dark wood cabinetry, granite countertops, a spacious pantry, stylish tile backsplash and Hardwood floors. Large windows complement the bright living room with its tall ceilings and cozy gas fireplace. The primary bedroom features an ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet, while the guest bedrooms share a large bath, all of which can be closed off with a modern barn door for added privacy. A versatile great room over the garage, converted into an additional bedroom with added closet space, is perfect for a home office or bonus living area. This home blends comfort, style and functionality in the peaceful Myers Estates' neighborhood.

Classic home on just shy 2-acre property with breathtaking mountain views! Boasting a newer metal roof, hardi-plank siding, huge trex deck, and a large fenced in area for dogs. Inside find a huge living room with vaulted ceilings with french doors. You also have a 3 head mini-split system for inexpensive heat and the bonus of A/C & a wood stove! Kitchen has lots of room to cook and also offers a vaulted ceiling. Bathroom has full tile shower and heated floors. Utility/sun room beams with light! So roomy & sunny you will actually want to do laundry! Upstairs being used as 3rd bedroom. Outside you have plenty of space for a garden and don't forget the apple & cherry trees! A nice dry outbuilding for storage or a shop & it has 220 power.

Nestled among the evergreens in the heart of beautiful Point Roberts is the perfect vacation get-a-way spot. Located directly across the street from a large undeveloped and wooded acreage this is truly versatile property. Can be used as your summer cabin, full time residence, Airbnb, or long-term rental. Open concept layout with living, dining, and kitchen. Property features two bedrooms, one bath and an airtight wood stove for cozy winter nights. The large, screened porch or Catio as it is affectionately called has numerous platforms and runways for your feline friends and lots of space for your patio furniture. Large storage shed and separate woodshed in the back yard. Come and enjoy the peace and tranquility of Point Roberts! Be sure to check out the online video tour.

A rare opportunity to own a quaint south beach two-bedroom + den, one-bath cottage on one of the most desirable streets in Point Roberts. Open concept floor plan with a propane fireplace in the heart of the cottage and a bright covered front porch. Sun-drenched private yard perfect for entertaining or garden space with a peek-a-boo ocean view. Only 30 minutes from Vancouver, the perfect vacation oasis.

Can you imagine building a NEW home in this trendy Bellingham neighborhood and being able to add an ADU to generate extra income? This zoning can accommodate your dreams as this house is a complete tear-down. There's no need to imagine anymore because this property is just a couple of blocks from the lively Trader Joe's area, minutes away from I-5, Barkley, and downtown Bellingham.

Presenting 2173 Northshore, a meticulously designed & built one-owner Lake Whatcom WATERFRONT estate. Sited on a .74 acre south-facing lot with 100 of private shoreline. Built in 2008, this stunning home spans 7005 SF & enjoys Brazilian cherry floors, views from the kitchen featuring a Subzero-Miele appliance package, a spacious main-level Primary Suite w/lake views, dual baths, walk-in closet + private balcony. Four additional BRs, office, 2 auxiliary rooms + a bonus room above the 3-car garage. The 720 SF boathouse features guest quarters & is sheltered from wind & waves by your own private, jetty-protected marina. Lake Whatcom waterfront at its finest. A mere visit is an experience; to live here is a dream come true.

This amazing 1-acre property with stunning views of the Canadian Mtns to the N & E is conveniently located yet very private, set back 1/4 mile from the road. The charming 2, 228 sqft rambler features an open concept design that seamlessly flows into a covered patio & outdoor kitchen, perfect for entertaining. Vaulted ceilings & abundant natural light create a warm & inviting atmosphere throughout the home. The spacious primary bedroom, complete with a cozy fireplace, provides a peaceful retreat. The property includes a 960 sqft shop for your projects, toys & tools, along with a private 250 sqft guest room/flex space & 1/2 bath above the garage. Raised flower beds provide ample space for your dream garden. Whole house generator included!

Great opportunity, come and see this 3 bedroom, 3 bath split level home on a beautiful secluded 6.55 acre parcel. Large fenced area for kenneling animals or maybe a protected garden area. Mature apple and pear fruit trees amid established landscaping will welcome you home. Convenient circular driveway and a spacious detached two car garage for your car or possibly a perfect spot to start a hobby. Close to both Bellingham and Ferndale making the commute to your work and extracurricular activities super easy. Park like setting.

Top floor condo with breathtaking sunsets and views of Bellingham Bay and the San Juan Islands. Ideally nestled above Boulevard Park, it offers convenient access to Fairhaven, downtown, South Bay boardwalk trail and interurban trail. The expansive interior showcases skylights in 3 rooms, a modern, updated kitchen with cherry cabinets, granite countertops and new appliances. The primary bath is a sanctuary with dual sinks, large walk-in multi-jet shower, and soaking tub all finished in Italian marble. Building amenities include an elevator, heated salt-water pool, sauna, laundry and clubhouse. Enjoy covered parking and two storage spaces. Don't miss visiting this beautifully updated view condo. By far the best unit with the best floor plan.

Brand new, quality built, 2 bedroom, 1.75 bathroom home with garage at the end of a cul-de-sac. Features include luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, stainless appliances, quartz counter tops, tile backsplash, mini-split unit that provides low cost heating with the benefits of A/C. Spacious kitchen with shaker style quality soft close cabinets. Brand new 2 bedroom septic system! No HOA. Large back yard and backs up to a greenbelt space and there is also a nice storage shed on property. Dead end cul-de-sac. Enjoy a brand new home about a 35 minute drive from Bellingham. Home has just been finished! One year builder warranty and garage has plug for electric car charging!

Welcome to The Ridge in Blaine, WA! This beautiful single-family home features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, offering comfortable, single-level living with no steps. The large, open main floor living area is perfect for modern lifestyles, and the covered back living area allows you to enjoy the outdoors year-round. High-end finishes include luxury vinyl flooring, quartz countertops, and a slab-on-grade foundation for low-maintenance living. This home backs up to a greenbelt, providing privacy and a serene natural backdrop. Conveniently located near downtown Blaine and I-5 for easy access to amenities. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity! $5, 000 Buyer Credit available with our preferred lender, Becky Farrar at Evergreen Home Loans.

Remodeled rambler in Birch Bay Village, a Pacific NW secure & gated all-ages community. Easy to fall in love w/ these modern finishes in a turn-key home. Flowing rambler floor plan, 3 beds, 2.5 baths, spacious living room w/ vaulted ceilings. Recent updates include: new kitchen, quartz counters, SS range + microwave + refrigerator + dishwasher, Luxury Vinyl Tile floors (waterproof), bathrooms, doors, trim, hardware, sliders, light fixtures, electrical, fresh paint inside & freshly landscape. Covered carport parking, driveway parking & extra enclosed storage space off carport. Large corner lot w/ neighborhood clubhouse, tennis & basketball & pickle ball courts, pool, golf course, boat launch, storage & marina w/ fuel dock.

Discover your private sanctuary in Ferndale - a charming 2-bedroom plus HUGE bonus room that could be used as a 3rd room or family room, nestled on almost 10 acres of mainly dry land. Whether you're dreaming of gardens, raising animals, developing or simply enjoying ultimate privacy, this property has it all. With ample space for RV parking or an ADU/shop development and no HOA, the possibilities are endless. Enjoy the fruit trees, nature and detached outbuilding with guests! Your long driveway sets far back from the main road, yielding maximum quiet enjoyment, making this is a rare find. Don't miss out on this unique opportunity in a highly sought out location!

MUST SEE immaculate 2007 40' Jayco Park Trailer on large, QUIET Div. 3 lot. The primary bedroom feels like a private retreat with a wall of windows that bring the outdoors in, while the second bedroom sleeps two adults and even more children! Slide outs make this already large trailer feel like home, and the permanent roof structure covers the trailer and a large deck for entertaining outside. A fenced gazebo serves as a covered firepit and a dog run, with two wood sheds nearby to keep you well stocked. The maintenance shed in back has many items and tools to help clean and maintain the property. Plenty of parking, and close to clubhouse, indoor pool, and all amenities. Come see why this lot puts the 'Paradise' in Campers Paradise!

Check out this gorgeous new home in Whispering Meadows! It's on a big lot and has 4 bedrooms, 2.25 bathrooms, and 1, 953 square feet. The kitchen has a spacious L-shaped countertop, a walk-in pantry, and stainless steel appliances. The dining room has a sliding door that leads to a covered deck and an awesome backyard for entertaining. The primary bedroom has an ensuite bathroom with a double vanity, quartz countertops, and a tile shower. Plus, there's a huge walk-in closet! The 4th bedroom over the garage could also be used as a bonus room. Ductless mini splits to keep you cool in the summer & warm in the winter.

Welcome to your beautifully crafted craftsman home complete with tall ceilings, west facing deck with french doors expand the living space to the out doors. The large screen windows throughout the home create a wonderful cross breeze and freshness in the home. Bask in the beautiful views of the South Fork Valley hills on both sides of the house. The house features unique touches such as Mexican sinks and tile. Enjoy a beautiful waterfall view on the Van Zandt dike in the colder winter months. Sunlight streams onto the property a majority of the day. Several mature wild cherry trees and raised garden bed, line the large yard. The perfect space for relaxing or entertaining your guests. Located near Van Zandt park and the South fork river.

Classic Fairhaven abode on fully master-gardener, landscaped lot. Updated throughout & totally charming! 3 bdrm, 1 full bath, luxury vinyl plank & tile flooring, all appliances stay. Double pane windows, affordable utilities, walking distance to the bay, Marine Park, Ferry Terminal events, train station and all of the Fairhaven shops. Warm, light-filled interior with amazing storage and efficient floor plan. Newer attached 24x16 garage, extra deep, is accessed off the alley w/more off road parking. Fenced back yard is totally private and has a patio for entertaining and a darling, multi-use studio outbuilding surrounded by lush greenery. This property is a charmer for sure, in excellent condition, and in a much sought after location.

BUYER BONUS AVAILABLE!! Introducing our exquisite 2-story Bluff floorplan featuring 3 beds & 2.75 bathrooms, and 2-car large tandem garage space. Enjoy the spacious deck off the main living area with breathtaking water views over Birch Bay. The primary suite is a true haven, boasting a lavish 5-piece ensuite with free standing tub, custom cabinets, and oversized walk-in closet creating ample space for all your needs. The lower level includes a bonus room for the perfect guest suite or entertainment space. Luxury abounds with ceramic tiles, and high-end appliances in the chef's dream kitchen. Proximity to golf clubs, Semiahmoo, Vancouver BC, and Seattle. Indulge in the epitome of elegance and coastal living. Your perfect oasis awaits.

This charming, single-level 3-bdrm, 2-bthrm home is ideal for first-time buyers or downsizers with over 1500 sqft of living space. The updated kitchen features solid Cherry wood cabinets, Marmoleum flooring, and quartz countertops. Enjoy the spacious dining rm, family rm, and living rm. Upgrades include a 50-year roof, vinyl windows, an expanded pantry w/ built-ins, updated appliances, a wood-burning stove, refinished hardwood floors, fresh interior paint, an updated primary en suite bathroom. The forced air heating ensures your comfort. The attached garage and fully fenced backyard w/ a patio and custom water fountain add to the appeal. Located close to the high school, Vista Middle School, and downtown Ferndale's restaurants and parks.

Edgewater Resort in Birch Bay is a convenient waterfront community offering both year-round and vacation living. Enjoy front-row views of Birch Bay from this 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath home! With 672 sq. ft. of cozy living space, this coastal retreat has updated both inside and out. Fresh interior and exterior paint, brand-new windows, and new flooring throughout. Step outside onto the freshly stained deck to soak in the water views. Storage shed offers additional space for your outdoor essentials.

Introducing a meticulously crafted 2024-built residence situated in Whispering Meadows Neighborhood in Nooksack. Discover Modern elegance finishes in a 3-bedroom + office/den w/ 3 full baths. Primary suite upstairs offers a his & her closet, bathroom w/ double vanity, step-in shower. Open kitchen is perfect for culinary enthusiasts, featuring an island, soft close cabinetry w/ large backyard views. The abundance of natural light enhances the space & allows your houseplants to thrive! Office/ den sits next to full bath on main floor. It features a covered front porch & covered deck.Spacious laundry room & ample storage throughout. Home offers the perfect blend of style, comfort, & convenience. Don't miss your chance-schedule your tour today!

One of the best views on the lake! 60+/- feet of low bank Lake Samish waterfront with a substantial private dock and lake water rights. Value in land, dock & water rights. All of the recreational pursuits await - waterskiing, fishing, kayaking, paddleboarding, swimming. Full view of the lake & foothills beyond. Original cabin with 1939 vintage wood paneling. Post & block foundation on .17 acre. Cabin is 576 SF with 2 BR & 3/4 BA. Come with your plans & ideas for future changes - remodel or new structure! Private well & property is on Lake Samish PUD sewer. This home & property are next to the Calmor Cove Club & you will turn into that property to get to the home. Property & home AS IS, stored items included.

Welcome to 'The Lake House, ' where every detail embodies the essence of luxury living. Tucked away from the road, a long driveway opens to a lawn with fruit trees and a pickleball court. This exquisite estate sits on 1.25 acres of beautifully landscaped ground with perfect sun exposure and 109 feet of lake frontage. Step into a world of true indoor-outdoor living where windows vanish into walls & the indoors flow out across the expansive lawn to the lake & dock. For those seeking the ultimate waterfront lifestyle, look no further. Every aspect of this home has been thoughtfully curated to provide the perfect blend of luxury & comfort. Sit back, relax, and immerse yourself in the beauty... after your morning glassy surf session, of course ;)

Step into contemporary luxury with this brand new home nestled in an old growth grove! Boasting an open concept layout, including a chic first-floor mother-in-law suite with private entrance. The suite is complete with a kitchenette, bedroom, and bathroom. The third floor reveals a private primary suite with three closet spaces and bonus room. Enjoy a serene escape on your private 300 sq ft deck surrounded by lush greenery, trail to Beaver Creek and old growth trees. Located in the convenient Gate 13, ten minutes from Bellingham with a flat road and easy winter access. An adventurer's dream, backing onto Stimpson Family Nature Reserve, walking distance to Lookout Mountain, an EV plug in and a 30 second bike ride to access Galbraith trails.

Discover waterfront luxury in Birch Bay Villages gated paradise. This custom-crafted home blends rich fir & cedar into a contemporary Northwest design. Cherish year-round vistas of Birch Bay, the Strait of Georgia, islands, and Mt. Baker. Spanning 3797 sq. ft. The layout includes main-level living, the Primary bedroom with additional office/bedroom, plus two upper suites, a loft, and a family room with a second kitchen. Radiant floor heating with multiple zones throughout. Air conditioning as well. Chefs kitchen, dining and Great room on the main level. Experience the pinnacle of waterfront living. Birch Bay Village amenities include 24/7 security, golf course, marina, clubhouse, pickleball, tennis, waterfront access, parks & more.

Nestled in a secluded enclave of luxury homes, this exquisite property boasts a manicured landscape complete w/ an irrigation system. The primary suite, conveniently located on the main level, features large dual closets & a lavish porcelain tile shower w/ dual heads. Soaring beamed ceilings define a spacious great room, anchored by a 50 gas fireplace set against a backdrop of matching stonework seen on the home's exterior. The gourmet kitchen is a chefs dream w/ cherry cabinets, a central island w/ prep sink, newer appliances, & granite countertops, lit by Hubberton hand-forged fixtures. Addl amenities include a 12KW generator, a heated oversized 2-car garage, a main-level office, bonus room, & generous covered porches. EV car charger.

Discover a cozy retreat in Ferndale with this charming 1-bedroom, 1-bath home. This home has been remodeled with new kitchen countertops, new appliances, and an updated bathroom layout. The laundry room has been updated with all new plumbing. Enjoy the outdoors on the new decks, one outside the bedroom and another off of the living room! The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting atmosphere for relaxation and entertainment. Situated on a sprawling acre of land, the property provides ample space for outdoor activities, gardening, and enjoying nature. Perfect for those seeking tranquility and convenience, this home is a hidden gem in a serene setting.

Fully serviced building lots ideal for your dream or spec home. 3 of 5 lots available. Lots 1, 2 and 4 - these are ready to go with water, sewer, power, gas and cable. Ft. Lot 4 is 9686 sq. ft. Some buffer reduction in place for lot 4. Established residential neighborhood with sidewalks and curbs. Nice affordable option for fully serviced ready to go building lots.

This setup can't be beat! The cozy trailer with add-a-room is set far back on the lot, giving you plenty of outdoor space. Whether you want to add a shed and/or gazebo, or maybe host more guests in a visiting RV, there's room. Inside sleeps 8 guests between the bedroom, bunk room and the addition which has a futon bunk bed. Bring everyone! There's a covered deck for dreary days and a paver patio around the fire pit for songs, stories and s'mores. A dine in kitchen and full bathroom, too. It's got everything you need to start making memories. Community amenities include two pools, parks, playgrounds, disc golf, tennis, Nooksack River access, 24/7 security and more. Limited to 120 days/year occupancy. No rentals.

First time on the market! This well-maintained home has 3 beds/1.75 baths and sits on a large lot that backs up to trees providing ultra privacy. The huge shop is a hobbyist's dream with multiple rooms/storage that you will never have to leave because it includes an additional shower and toilet! Amazing location - 5 minutes to the border, Birch Bay, and Semiahmoo Resort. Located in the Sunday Harbor community, which offers a boat launch, playground, picnic area, and fire pit on California Creek. A heat pump ensures you stay cool during the hot summer and warm during the cold winter. This is your chance to own a home, shop, and a 10K sq. ft. lot for $375K! Home is being sold by Power of Attorney - buyer to verify all information.

Opportunity is Knocking! Great potential for the project minded individual. This two bedroom, two bath home is being sold "As Is", all contents included - A Garage Sale Enthusiasts Paradise. Property has a Water Meter, and the Septic system just passed inspection with flying colours. Walking distance to all amenities: beaches, parks, community centers, post offices, restaurants, library, grocery store, gas stations and even the marina. This won't last long! Check out link to online video tour.

Experience the beauty of South Hill in this stunning home with breathtaking views! Inspired by Frank Lloyd Wright, this stylish residence boasts bamboo hardwood floors, two gas fireplaces, stainless steel appliances & honed black quartz waterfall countertops in the kitchen. The abundance of skylights & windows fills the home with natural light. The main level offers everything you need, including a primary suite with a view & private deck access. The lower level provides spacious family room, two bedrooms, full bathroom & separate outdoor entrance. With a private driveway & stairway access from Morey Ave, convenience is key. The low-maintenance yard includes a covered, fenced area under the deck. Move in, relax & savor stunning sunsets!

This is the full lakefront package! The Fairhaven design is the largest tiny home, no joke. Features a spacious living and kitchen area, a front deck for sunshine, and a covered deck with Infratech heaters great for entertaining. Explore this unique layout with a two-bedroom loft, upper fireplace, and incredible rooftop deck for excellent star gazing. This includes a deep water boat slip in the Wildwood Marina, and access to all of the community resort amenities. If you are a busy professional who is looking for an easy, fun, and safe property in a vacation resort community of like-minded lake enthusiasts - schedule a private tour!

Quality construction and care is evident throughout this park model with add-a-room at the Glen at Maple Falls! Energy/efficiency updates include two heat pumps for heating and cooling, an additional electrical panel and an upgraded furnace. Bedroom on the main floor with additional sleeping space in the loft. Full bath and full size appliances in the kitchen. Covered deck for year-round enjoyment and a storage shed. Comes fully furnished and ready to go! Community amenities include Nooksack River access, parks, trails, pools, playgrounds, disc golf & year-round events. Gated access w/ 24/7 security. Located just 30 minutes form Bellingham & 15 minutes from the base of Mt. Baker & Silver Lake. Limited to 120 days/year occupancy. No rentals.

This charming 3-bedroom, 1.75-bathroom home offers serene living in a quiet Lynden location, situated on an expansive 13, 500 square foot, flat lot. The home has been tastefully remodeled and is move-in ready, featuring a gorgeous kitchen with ample cabinet space, a separate dining room perfect for gatherings, and a cozy, clean interior. The primary bedroom is conveniently located on the main floor, while two additional bedrooms are upstairs, along with a 3/4 bath. Unfinished 900 sq ft basement too! Outside, you'll find a detached 3-car garage with plenty of RV parking. This home offers peaceful living with ample outdoor space to relax, play, or entertain. Clean and well-maintained, it's a true gem!

Charming one-level country-style home boasts 3 bedrooms, 1 bath, and a bonus room on nearly 5 acres of land. The property includes a spacious 30'X50' shop, ideal for various uses. Situated conveniently close to Bellingham and other attractions, this home offers the perfect blend of county living with urban convenience. Inside you will find a large family and dining room area, skylights for natural light, a well appointed kitchen with all new appliances and an island. Step outside to enjoy a peaceful pond and views of Mt. Baker from back deck, which features upgrade trex decking (front and back). Equestrian and other possibilities...Come and see this amazing place.

Great location on the 7th fairway! This custom-built home in the Stonehaven neighborhood of Semiahmoo is just what you have been waiting for. The great room features an open kitchen, vaulted ceilings, and French doors that open to a raised patio. The main floor includes a primary suite, a private guest suite, and a media room/den. Upstairs, a bright bonus room with a bath serves as additional guest quarters or a home office. The home has been well-maintained, with a new roof in 2023, a stack stone fireplace, & air conditioning. The beautifully landscaped yard completes this wonderful property. Easy access to all resort amenities - golf, pickleball, tennis & health club. Enjoy the best of Semiahmoo living in this lovely, move-in-ready home!

Rare opportunity to purchase nearly 4.3 acres of land in the highly sought-after Meridian School District. This property offers all utilities on site & includes a 1, 782 square foot manufactured home featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Situated at the end of E Axton, just beyond the bend on Starry Road, the property boasts a serene & secluded setting surrounded by natural beauty and mature trees. Enjoy the peaceful, country atmosphere while being just a short 15-minute drive from Lynden and Bellingham & minutes away from the scenic Shuksan Golf Course. The area offers a perfect blend of tranquility & convenience, with access to local farms, parks & outdoor recreation, making this property truly unique with endless possibilities.
